data.text:
Day Time 6:00 PM to 8:00 PM Where Private Location (sign in to display)

Did you know that Binghamton?s Football Team has been undefeated since 1946? Did you know that the board game Monopoly was originally invented in 1935? Come test your trivia knowledge (& luck) at Delta Sigma Pi?s trivia night!
